   "source": [
    "# 终极全能智能体 · 第一阶段第2天\n",
    "## 梯度下降与反向传播算法\n",
    "\n",
    "### 学习目标\n",
    "1. 深入理解梯度下降算法原理\n",
    "2. 掌握反向传播算法的数学推导\n",
    "3. 实现手动梯度下降和反向传播\n",
    "4. 理解神经网络训练的核心机制\n",
    "5. 应用算法解决XOR问题\n",
    "\n",
    "### 环境检查"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import sys\n",
    "import os\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"PyTorch版本: {torch.__version__}\")\n",
    "print(f\"NumPy版本: {np.__version__}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Python版本: {sys.version}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 添加项目路径\n",
    "sys.path.append(os.path.join(os.getcwd(), 'src/algorithms/day02_gradient_backprop'))\n",
    "\n",
    "# 检查CUDA是否可用\n",
    "print(f\"CUDA可用: {torch.cuda.is_available()}\")\n",
    "if torch.cuda.is_available():\n",
    "    print(f\"CUDA设备: {torch.cuda.get_device_name(0)}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 第一部分：梯度下降算法\n",
    "\n",
    "梯度下降是优化神经网络参数的核心算法。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 导入梯度下降演示类\n",
    "from gradient_descent_demo import GradientDescentDemo\n",
    "\n",
    "# 创建演示实例\n",
    "demo = GradientDescentDemo()\n",
    "\n",
    "# 生成测试数据\n",
    "X, y = demo.generate_data(n_samples=100)\n",
    "print(f\"数据形状: X={X.shape}, y={y.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"真实参数: w=2.0, b=3.0\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1.1 梯度计算演示"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 计算初始梯度\n",
    "w, b = 0.0, 0.0\n",
    "dw, db = demo.compute_gradients(w, b, X, y)\n",
    "initial_loss = demo.compute_loss(w, b, X, y)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"初始参数: w={w}, b={b}\")\n",
    "print(f\"初始损失: {initial_loss:.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"初始梯度: dw={dw:.4f}, db={db:.4f}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1.2 执行梯度下降"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 执行梯度下降\n",
    "w_final, b_final, history = demo.gradient_descent(\n",
    "    X, y, \n",
    "    learning_rate=0.01, \n",
    "    n_iterations=100,\n",
    "    initial_w=0.0,\n",
    "    initial_b=0.0\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"最终参数: w={w_final:.4f}, b={b_final:.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"最终损失: {history[-1]['loss']:.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"损失减少: {((initial_loss - history[-1]['loss']) / initial_loss * 100):.1f}%\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1.3 可视化梯度下降过程"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 可视化梯度下降\n",
    "fig = demo.visualize_gradient_descent(X, y, history)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1.4 学习率比较"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 比较不同学习率\n",
    "demo.compare_learning_rates(X, y)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 第二部分：反向传播算法\n",
    "\n",
    "反向传播是神经网络训练的核心算法，使用链式法则计算梯度。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 导入反向传播演示类\n",
    "from backpropagation_demo import SimpleNeuralNetwork, BackpropagationVisualizer\n",
    "\n",
    "# 创建可视化器\n",
    "visualizer = BackpropagationVisualizer()\n",
    "\n",
    "# 生成XOR问题数据\n",
    "X, y = visualizer.generate_xor_data()\n",
    "print(f\"XOR问题数据:\")\n",
    "print(f\"输入:\\n{X}\")\n",
    "print(f\"输出:\\n{y}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.1 创建神经网络"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 创建神经网络\n",
    "nn = SimpleNeuralNetwork(input_size=2, hidden_size=3, output_size=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"网络结构: 输入层({nn.input_size}) -> 隐藏层({nn.hidden_size}) -> 输出层({nn.output_size})\")\n",
    "print(f\"权重形状: W1={nn.W1.shape}, W2={nn.W2.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"偏置形状: b1={nn.b1.shape}, b2={nn.b2.shape}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.2 前向传播演示"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 前向传播\n",
    "y_pred_initial = nn.forward(X)\n",
    "initial_loss = nn.compute_loss(y_pred_initial, y)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"初始预测:\\n{y_pred_initial}\")\n",
    "print(f\"初始损失: {initial_loss:.6f}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 可视化神经网络结构\n",
    "visualizer.visualize_neural_network(nn, X, y)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.3 单步反向传播演示"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 反向传播\n",
    "gradients = nn.backward(X, y, y_pred_initial)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"梯度计算完成:\")\n",
    "print(f\"dW1形状: {gradients['dW1'].shape}, 范数: {np.linalg.norm(gradients['dW1']):.6f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"dW2形状: {gradients['dW2'].shape}, 范数: {np.linalg.norm(gradients['dW2']):.6f}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 可视化梯度\n",
    "visualizer.visualize_backpropagation_step(nn, gradients)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.4 训练神经网络"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 训练神经网络\n",
    "history = nn.train(X, y, learning_rate=0.5, n_iterations=1000, verbose=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 训练后评估\n",
    "y_pred_final = nn.forward(X)\n",
    "final_loss = nn.compute_loss(y_pred_final, y)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n训练结果:\")\n",
    "print(f\"最终预测:\\n{y_pred_final}\")\n",
    "print(f\"最终损失: {final_loss:.6f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"损失减少: {((initial_loss - final_loss) / initial_loss * 100):.1f}%\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.5 可视化训练历史"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 可视化训练历史\n",
    "visualizer.visualize_training_history(history)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 第三部分：PyTorch自动梯度\n",
    "\n",
    "PyTorch提供了自动微分功能，简化了梯度计算。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# PyTorch自动梯度演示\n",
    "x = torch.tensor(2.0, requires_grad=True)\n",
    "w = torch.tensor(3.0, requires_grad=True)\n",
    "b = torch.tensor(1.0, requires_grad=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 前向传播\n",
    "y = w * x + b\n",
    "\n",
    "# 计算损失\n",
    "target = torch.tensor(10.0)\n",
    "loss = (y - target) ** 2\n",
    "\n",
    "# 反向传播\n",
    "loss.backward()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"计算图: y = {w.item()} * {x.item()} + {b.item()} = {y.item()}\")\n",
    "print(f\"损失: {loss.item():.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"梯度: dx/dw = {x.grad.item():.4f}, dloss/dw = {w.grad.item():.4f}, dloss/db = {b.grad.item():.4f}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 第四部分：关键概念总结\n",
    "\n",
    "### 4.1 梯度下降关键概念\n",
    "1. **梯度 (Gradient)**: 损失函数对参数的偏导数\n",
    "2. **学习率 (Learning Rate)**: 控制参数更新步长\n",
    "3. **批量梯度下降**: 使用全部数据计算梯度\n",
    "4. **随机梯度下降**: 使用单个样本计算梯度\n",
    "5. **小批量梯度下降**: 使用小批量数据计算梯度\n",
    "6. **动量 (Momentum)**: 加速收敛，减少震荡\n",
    "7. **自适应学习率**: Adam, RMSprop等优化器\n",
    "\n",
    "### 4.2 反向传播关键公式\n",
    "1. **输出层梯度**: $\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial Z_2} = (A_2 - Y) \\odot \\sigma'(Z_2)$\n",
    "2. **隐藏层梯度**: $\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial Z_1} = (\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial Z_2} \\cdot W_2^T) \\odot \\sigma'(Z_1)$\n",
    "3. **权重梯度**: \n",
    "   - $\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial W_2} = A_1^T \\cdot \\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial Z_2}$\n",
    "   - $\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial W_1} = X^T \\cdot \\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial Z_1}$\n",
    "4. **偏置梯度**: \n",
    "   - $\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial b_2} = \\sum \\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial Z_2}$\n",
    "   - $\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial b_1} = \\sum \\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial Z_1}$\n",
    "\n",
    "### 4.3 链式法则\n",
    "反向传播的核心是链式法则：\n",
    "$$\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial W} = \\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial A} \\cdot \\frac{\\partial A}{\\partial Z} \\cdot \\frac{\\partial Z}{\\partial W}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "## 第五部分：实战练习\n",
    "\n",
    "### 练习1：实现动量梯度下降\n",
    "在梯度下降基础上添加动量项：\n",
    "$$v_t = \\beta v_{t-1} + (1-\\beta) \\nabla_\\theta J(\\theta)$$\n",
    "$$\\theta = \\theta - \\eta v_t$$\n",
    "\n",
    "### 练习2：实现Adam优化器\n",
    "结合动量和自适应学习率：\n",
    "1. 计算一阶矩估计（动量）\n",
    "2. 计算二阶矩估计（自适应学习率）\n",
    "3. 偏差修正\n",
    "4. 参数更新\n",
    "\n",
    "### 练习3：实现三层神经网络\n",
    "扩展为输入层-隐藏层1-隐藏层2-输出层结构\n",
    "\n",
    "## 第六部分：学习总结\n",
    "\n",
    "### 今日收获\n",
    "1. ✅ 掌握了梯度下降算法的原理和实现\n",
    "2. ✅ 理解了反向传播的数学推导\n",
    "3. ✅ 实现了手动梯度计算和参数更新\n",
    "4. ✅ 学会了使用PyTorch自动微分\n",
    "5. ✅ 解决了经典的XOR问题\n",
    "\n",
    "### 明日预告\n",
    "**第3天：多层感知机（MLP） + Dropout**\n",
    "1. 实现完整的MLP网络\n",
    "2. 理解Dropout正则化原理\n",
    "3. 应用MLP解决更复杂的问题\n",
    "\n",
